（以下简称长城汽车）因「供货商发生重大失信行为，且影响恶劣」被列为「不接受投标」供应商，处理期限为 24 个月。 大河财立方记者联系到长城汽车工作人员询问该事件具体情况，对方表示，以官方消息为准。 长城汽车曾多次参与南方电网旗下公司招标，最近一次为 2022 年 11 月，长城汽车中标南方电网电动汽车服务有限公司 2022—2024 年度通用车辆（第一批）框架采购。南方电网「拉黑」长城汽车：发生重大失信行为，且影响恶劣"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-f60e1cb3d5762c8db2bed3e65263f282_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "607 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664796341"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIz8aQhZ3XgpVNEAMaCTExMDAwOTk2OCCoi5G2BjAAOL0BQAJyCTY2NDc5NjM0MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1724231444.675629", "card_id": "Q_51075975", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 204}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我为什么总觉得辛弃疾用典的词写的很一般，而不用典的写的很好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "感觉辛弃疾的《丑奴儿》《清平乐》《青玉案》都写的极好，但像《水龙吟》之类的就不是很好，很难引起共鸣。――――――――――――――呐呐诸位我哪里敢说他老人家写的不好，我是说没他不用典的写的好，大家注意审题哈。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-013737f54f0a519018b123802a85b23b_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "207 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/51075975"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iz8aQhZ3XgpVNEAMaCDEyNjQ3ODQyIOvIqr8FMAA4nglAA3IINTEwNzU5NzV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1724231444.675983", "card_id": "Q_664065760", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {